## What the tests cover and why

| Category | Tests | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| **Authentication** | Unauthenticated users are rejected; service & audit are never called | Requirement gate: *authenticated* manager only |
| **Authorization** | Non-manager role raises `AuthorizationError` | Requirement gate: *manager* role only |
| **Mandatory field validation** | Each of the 5 fields is independently omitted; blank strings treated as missing; all errors aggregated; dates cross-checked | Requirement: *mandatory fields must be validated* |
| **Successful creation** | Correct service call, correct payload, `PENDING` status, returns the created object | Happy-path proof |
| **Audit record** | Written once, after service create, with correct actor/action/resource/resource-id/metadata; NOT written on service error or validation failure | Requirement: *audit record written on success* |
| **Edge cases** | Extra form fields ignored, long text, all leave types, no double-submission | Robustness |
